      "span_text": "The changes of macroscopic properties induced by the gold ions irradiation can be compared with the recent results obtained by Karakurt with 7 MeV Au ions irradiation [CITATION_1] which showed a decrease of hardness of similar amplitude, −38% compared to −36% in our study, and a decrease of density that seems to be higher, −2.7% compared to −1.6% in this study.",
